im in the crypt. There left him.\x{2019}<<Six in the morning|5>>, a Wednesday, the feast of St Andrew the Apostle. I, a simple cardinal. There left him and rode south, to find the king at Hampton Court. Who says to George, \x{2018}I would not for twenty thousand pounds that the cardinal had died.\x{2019}\x{2018}Look, Cavendish,\x{2019} he says, \x{2018}when you are asked what the cardinal said in his last days, tell them nothing.\x{2019}George raises his eyebrows. \x{2018}I already have. Told them nothing. The king questioned me. My lord Norfolk.\x{2019}\x{2018}If you tell Norfolk anything, he will twist it into treason.\x{2019}\x{2018}Still, as he is Lord Treasurer, he has paid me my back wages. I was three-quarters of the year in arrears.\x{2019}\x{2018}What were you paid, George?\x{2019}\x{2018}Ten pounds a year.\x{2019}\x{2018}You should have come to me.\x{2019}These are the facts. These are the figures. If the Lord of the Underworld rose up tomorrow in the privy chamber, and offered a dead man back, fresh from the grave, fresh from the crypt, the miracle of Lazarus for \x{a3}20,000 \x{2013} Henry Tudor would be pushed to scrape it together. Norfolk as Lord Treasurer? Fine; it doesn't matter who holds the title, who holds the clanking keys to the empty chests.\x{2018}Do you know,\x{2019} he says, \x{2018}if the cardinal could say, as he used to say to me, Thomas, what would you like for a New Year's gift, I would say, I would like sight of the nation's accounts.\x{2019}Cavendish hesitates; he begins to speak; he stops; he starts again. \x{2018}The king said certain things to me. At Hampton Court. \x{201c}Three may keep counsel, if two are away.\x{201d}\x{2019}\x{2018}It is a proverb, I think.\x{2019}\x{2018}He said, \x{201c}If I thought my cap knew my counsel, I would cast it into the fire.\x{201d}\x{2019}\x{2018}I think that also is a proverb.\x{2019}\x{2018}He means to say that he will not choose any adviser now: not my lord of Norfolk, nor Stephen Gardiner, o